wherein:
R1, R2, R3 and R4 are independently represented as described below:
n=1
R1=R2=CH3—(CH2)10CH2—, CH3—(CH2)12CH2—, CH3—(CH2)14 CH2—, CH3—, (CH2)16 CH2— and/or CH3—(CH2)7—CH═CH(CH2)7CH2—;
